      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Generative AI, that can generate answer on its own, It is not like that we have ask a question and\nfor that there is a fixed answer, if we have given question that it has never seen before still it\ncan generate answer of that. using finding pattern on tokens.",
