      "text": "Q What is the temprature in Delhi today?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q What is the temprature in Delhi today?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jyvQ_Qfl-hxYV9pjuxXIq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 950.0342489213419,
      "y": 46316.96583955291,
      "width": 1265,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 260927229,
      "version": 118,
      "versionNonce": 16845680,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Today in Delhi, it’s extremely hot 🔥\n\n🌡️ Maximum temperature: around 41–44°C\n🌙 Minimum temperature: around 26–31°C\n\n👉 Recent reports also mention a heatwave, with temperatures already touching 43°C+ in parts of the city.\n\nIn short:\nIt’s a very hot day, typical peak summer conditions—avoid going out in the afternoon if possible and stay hydrated.\n\nIf you want, I can give you \nhourly temperature or \ncompare it with Lucknow today.\n\nfor this answer it has taken external help like news updates and weather service.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Today in Delhi, it’s extremely hot 🔥\n\n🌡️ Maximum temperature: around 41–44°C\n🌙 Minimum temperature: around 26–31°C\n\n👉 Recent reports also mention a heatwave, with temperatures already touching 43°C+ in parts of the city.\n\nIn short:\nIt’s a very hot day, typical peak summer conditions—avoid going out in the afternoon if possible and stay hydrated.\n\nIf you want, I can give you \nhourly temperature or \ncompare it with Lucknow today.\n\nfor this answer it has taken external help like news updates and weather service.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TGIKYHPrLYTEjr5Q4Gl2d",
