      "text": "LLM can only predict, then can't run the code, they can't calculate etc.\nModern LLM will not perform all the tasks themselves like calculation, what is going on internet, anything\nto fetch data from the internet so for that they take help of external tool.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LLM can only predict, then can't run the code, they can't calculate etc.\nModern LLM will not perform all the tasks themselves like calculation, what is going on internet, anything\nto fetch data from the internet so for that they take help of external tool.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "u1CKrDjUX85nNf_QN0T2t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 977.9837631692194,
