      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "from google import genai\n\n\nclient = genai.Client(api_key=\"AIzaSyCiaVzwz9Kg_LHDl9JuhRE5MKOFtMDlnis\")\n\nresponse = client.models.generate_content(\n    model=\"gemini-3-flash-preview\", contents=\"anything\"\n)\nprint(response.text)\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "from google import genai\n\n\nclient = genai.Client(api_key=\"AIzaSyCiaVzwz9Kg_LHDl9JuhRE5MKOFtMDlnis\")\n\nresponse = client.models.generate_content(\n    model=\"gemini-3-flash-preview\", contents=\"anything\"\n)\nprint(response.text)\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8Bw9yNHRnFcBuYiIx3Z-s",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 938.9201112459864,
      "y": 49748.40317360525,
      "width": 2057,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1033937875,
      "version": 396,
      "versionNonce": 199734672,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "content 1 -> Hi I am Rohit\n    response -> Hi Rohit! It’s nice to meet you. How can I help you today?\n\ncontent 2-> tell me my name and age\n    response -> I don't know your name or age. As an AI, I don’t have access to your personal identity, private documents, or account details unless you specifically tell me who you are. \n                If you'd like, you can tell me your name, and I will remember it for the rest of our conversation!\n\n\nHence Pure LLM doesnt store anything, LLM can't store any previous state.\n\nLLM can tell answer on the basis of context that we have given.\n\n\ncontent3 -> HI I am Rohit, What is my Name\n response -> Rohit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "content 1 -> Hi I am Rohit\n    response -> Hi Rohit! It’s nice to meet you. How can I help you today?\n\ncontent 2-> tell me my name and age\n    response -> I don't know your name or age. As an AI, I don’t have access to your personal identity, private documents, or account details unless you specifically tell me who you are. \n                If you'd like, you can tell me your name, and I will remember it for the rest of our conversation!\n\n\nHence Pure LLM doesnt store anything, LLM can't store any previous state.\n\nLLM can tell answer on the basis of context that we have given.\n\n\ncontent3 -> HI I am Rohit, What is my Name\n response -> Rohit",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nF7FYG85kOuwWcAQVvwT5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 942.6277827236111,
      "y": 50177.74919394641,
      "width": 385,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1535719347,
      "version": 53,
      "versionNonce": 1338256240,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If we ask same things from ChatGPT ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If we ask same things from ChatGPT ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yLZiVBe42ws-Y-NuffeTU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 978.9216803076299,
      "y": 50217.5871892664,
      "width": 1144,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bXr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 959366365,
      "version": 643,
      "versionNonce": 511345552,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777053178243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1 I am ROhit -> response -> Hi rohit how are you and all\n2 What is my name -> response -> Rohit\n3 Can you guess my parents name -> Sorry I can't\n\nHow it is happening?\n    ChatGPT behind the scene not only sending last question to LLM model, it is sending all the question\nthat we have asked also what was response for that + new question so LLM has all the context of our \nchat. We see if we ask in same window it will give correct answer but in next window it will give\nwrong response hence it is only sending one window context to LLM.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 I am ROhit -> response -> Hi rohit how are you and all\n2 What is my name -> response -> Rohit\n3 Can you guess my parents name -> Sorry I can't\n\nHow it is happening?\n    ChatGPT behind the scene not only sending last question to LLM model, it is sending all the question\nthat we have asked also what was response for that + new question so LLM has all the context of our \nchat. We see if we ask in same window it will give correct answer but in next window it will give\nwrong response hence it is only sending one window context to LLM.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "P6P2b_pvCpI4UyKsoNOeN",
      "type": "text",
